title: The Grateful Dead Live at The Zenith on 1990-10-28
description:
Set 1

Touch Of Gray, Walkin' Blues, Candyman, Box Of Rain, Mexicali Blues, Maggie's Farm, Althea, Cassidy, Tennessee Jed, Stander on the Mountain

Set 2

Victim Or The Crime, Eyes Of The World-> Estimated Prophet-> Uncle John's Band-> Drums-> Jam-> The Other One-> Wharf Rat-> Sugar Magnolia, E: Knockin' On Heaven's Door

reviews.review_text: Better than sdb I love this guys recordings makes me feel like I'm at the show so thank u Andrew k thanks for all the great recordings & shared em with all of us smoking 2nd set
